Chapter 3, Example 1

Create an Image file:
kevin@Ubuntu:~/kernel/linux-0.11/tst/ch3/1$ bximage 

#kevin@Ubuntu:~/kernel/linux-0.11/tst/ch3/1$ dd if=boot of=a.img bs=512 count=2880
kevin@Ubuntu:~/kernel/linux-0.11/tst/ch3/1$ dd bs=32 if=boot of=a.img skip=1

kevin@Ubuntu:~/kernel/linux-0.11/tst/ch3/1$ bochs -q -f bochsrc-fda.bxrc
